id: hac-l25p
title: Auto-release dry run omits pm-changelog installation on clean runners
description: "The exact-master non-publishing Auto Release dispatch fails on a clean GitHub runner because scripts/release/auto-release.mjs skips installLatestChangelog() when --dry-run is set, then invokes an unavailable pm changelog command."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[7]: automation,changelog,dry-run,github-actions,pm-changelog,production-follow-up,release
created_at: "2026-07-21T21:11:50.143Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-21T21:23:14.573Z"
deadline: "2026-07-22T21:11:50.143Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-21T21:23:02.938Z"
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 45
acceptance_criteria: "A clean-runner workflow_dispatch with dry_run=true and allow_same_day_release=true installs the latest pm-changelog, generates the candidate changelog, completes all release gates, and does not commit, tag, push, or publish"
definition_of_ready: Exact failed workflow job log identifies Unknown command changelog after the dry-run-only installation branch
goal: lossless-automatic-releases
objective: clean-runner-dry-run-parity
value: Keep the non-publishing release rehearsal trustworthy on clean infrastructure.
impact: Prevents false release failures and ensures scheduled release prerequisites are exercised before publication.
outcome: Hosted auto-release dry runs complete end to end while preserving their no-publish contract.
why_now: Exact final master proof run 29868743104 exposed the clean-runner gap.
parent: hac-wwsi
reviewer: unbraind
risk: high
confidence: high
release: 2026.7.22
reporter: codex-root
severity: high
environment: GitHub Actions Auto Release workflow_dispatch on a clean ubuntu runner
repro_steps: "Dispatch auto-release.yml on master with push=false, dry_run=true, allow_same_day_release=true; observe scripts/release/auto-release.mjs invoke pm changelog without first installing pm-changelog."
resolution: Provision pm-changelog in both release modes and install pinned clean-runner verification prerequisites before the Auto Release pipeline.
expected_result: "Hosted dry-run provisions the changelog generator and complete verification toolchain, then validates a release candidate without publishing."
actual_result: "Fresh local clone and hosted run 29869474842 completed the entire candidate pipeline; pushed=false and no commit, tag, package, or release was created."
affected_version: 2026.7.21-2
fixed_version: 2026.7.22
component: release-automation
regression: false
customer_impact: No publication occurred; maintainers cannot rely on the hosted dry-run rehearsal.
dependencies[3]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  hac-9hs1,related,"2026-07-21T21:11:50.143Z",null,null
  hac-m1kj,related,"2026-07-21T21:11:50.143Z",null,null
  hac-n0ix,discovered_from,"2026-07-21T21:11:50.143Z",null,null
comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T21:11:50.143Z",codex-root,"Exact public evidence: https://github.com/unbraind/homeassistant-cli/actions/runs/29868743104 job 88763366091. The failure occurs before version mutation or publication and contains no private data."
  "2026-07-21T21:18:37.608Z",codex-root,"First hosted repair run 29869217387 proved pm-changelog now installs and generation starts on a clean runner. The full release gate then exposed missing runner prerequisites: scripts/release/verify-release.sh could not find rg or trivy. The workflow now provisions ripgrep, shellcheck, and the current official setup-trivy v0.3.1 pinned to commit 81e5143, with current Trivy v0.72.0."
  "2026-07-21T21:23:00.827Z",codex-root,"Final hosted acceptance proof: Auto Release run https://github.com/unbraind/homeassistant-cli/actions/runs/29869474842 succeeded on exact branch head fb2b6af7810e5102f01152fdd082f90218e4a6ca. It installed latest pm-changelog, ripgrep, ShellCheck, and pinned Trivy; completed all release gates and packed npm/Bun smoke; produced a dry-run candidate only, with no commit, tag, push, or publication."
  "2026-07-21T21:23:14.573Z",codex-root,"The recorded failed linked-test run is not a product regression: pm 2026.7.21 --only-last selected the older test instead of the newly added hosted assertion. Existing upstream issue https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/515 was found before filing; the current-version reproduction was added there, and explicit --only-index 1 passed."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T21:11:50.143Z",codex-root,Keep dry-run non-publishing. Installing a build-time pm extension is permitted; commit/tag/push/package publication remain disabled.
learnings[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T21:11:50.143Z",codex-root,Clean local workspaces can mask missing extension provisioning because pm-changelog is already installed; release rehearsals require clean-runner proof.
  "2026-07-21T21:23:01.504Z",codex-root,A release workflow must provision every tool used transitively by its aggregate verification script. Green standalone CI jobs do not put their binaries into a separate Auto Release runner.
files[2]{path,scope,note}:
  scripts/release/auto-release.mjs,project,Provision latest pm-changelog before both dry-run and release generation
  .github/workflows/auto-release.yml,project,Hosted exact-master reproduction and proof
tests[2]:
  - command: "test \"$(gh run view 29869474842 --json conclusion --jq .conclusion)\" = success"
    scope: project
    timeout_seconds: 60
    note: Exact branch clean-runner Auto Release dry run succeeds without publication
  - command: node scripts/release/auto-release.mjs --dry-run --json --allow-same-day-release
    path: scripts/release/auto-release.mjs
    scope: project
    timeout_seconds: 1200
    note: Exercise full non-publishing release candidate
test_runs[2]{run_id,kind,status,started_at,finished_at,recorded_at,passed,failed,skipped}:
