close_reason: Clean-runner dry-run now completes the full release and package-smoke pipeline without publishing.
body: "## Evidence\\n\\nExact master run 29868743104 failed before version mutation or publication with Unknown command changelog.\\n\\n## Definition of done\\n\\n- Provision latest pm-changelog in dry-run and publishing paths.\\n- Pass local and clean hosted non-publishing rehearsal.\\n- Retain zero commit, tag, push, or package publication in dry-run mode."
